data.description: Hello Gorgeous This Charming Spanish Ranch style home  is very spacious with large bedrooms, kitchen and living spaces! Grand Arched Windows in Great Room,  Freshly Painted Interior Spanish Fly textured walls, Cul-De-Sac Street. Outside you will notice the huge, fully fenced in yard with Gunite POOL! Great for entertaining, doors from the kitchen lead to a back porch patio that is partially covered. Home offers double carport. Spacious Side Yards.  Owner's Suite w/Huge Walk-In Closets boasts subway tiled shower in the bathroom, additional bedrooms located convenient to another full bathroom. 4th Bedroom was could be 2nd master with Jacuzzi Tub and separate shower.  Convenient To Fort Gordon, Plant Voglt, Airport, Shopping and Dining...WELCOME HOME!
